## Limitations

The findings are based on available online resources and may not encompass all perspectives on the topic. The search was limited to English-language sources, which may exclude relevant information from non-English publications. Additionally, the dynamic nature of media and technology means that the impact on career knowledge is continually evolving, and newer studies may provide further insights.

